<h1>Scope of Work</h1>
<p>This report was written and compiled using information retrieved from the Nova Scotia Property Online system, published by the Province of Nova Scotia. The intention was to clearly demonstrate the chain of title of an assigned subject report.<i>See</i> <a href="#docs">[Appendix A - Documents]</a>. Additional resources were retrieved from the internet. <i>See</i> <a href="#refs">[Appendix B - References]</a>.</p>
<p>This webpage was written and compiled using PHP, HTML, CSS and Javascript. Templating is based on the front-end web framework Bootstrap. Tables are formatted using the jQuery plugin DataTables. Maps are displayed using the Google Maps API. Fonts (Inconsolata and Roboto) provided by Google Fonts.</p>


